2001-05-24  olicha  <olivier.chapuis@free.fr>

	* themes/default/functions:
	* themes/default/menu:
	* themes/default/bindings:
	Some Maximizing works. Added some "simple" functions and use it.
	In the Maximize Menu use "On" in the place of the implicite toggle.
	Note: unfortunately, the Grow maximizing seems buggy in fvwm,
	"incremental" Grow does not work.

	* themes/*/buttons:
 	Use the FuncFvwmMaximize{,Vertically,Horizontally} functions,
	in the place of hard coded analogue, Shift All on maximize
	button give Grow (as lutien) and fix the ShowInfo for the max
	buttons
	
2001-05-24  migo  <migo@homemail.com>

	* themes/default/menus-programs:
	don't recreate xlock menus on every read (it may take 3 seconds!),
	instead create on request (and only once), much faster :)

