2001-04-08  migo  <migo@homemail.com>

	* NEWS:
	* themes/nanogui:
	After a lot of internal twicking added nanogui theme with components
	buttons@, colors-extra@ and windowlook@.
	Using of colors-extra@ is only temporary, I hope.
	buttons@ has a really nice titlebar button selector.
	Image stick*.xpm was originally named hide*.xpm, but I don't know
	what "hide" should do, so I changed it.
	Images shade*.xpm were originally named roll*.xpm.

