	Fixed the name of the start menu

	* themes/redmond98/modules/main:startmenu:
	Some update vs the default menu

	* themes/redmond98/modules/taskbarpos:
	* themes/olicha/modules/main:FvwmTaskBar
	"Fixed" the position of the start menu for bottom task bar
	Ok, ok ... I use the taskbar and I almost always resize it, thus
	the position menu have to be computed from the taskbar window,
	but the Window (and other contexts) does not work in fvwm2 or I
	do not understand how it work!
	So, the only solution is to use a position relatively to the mouse.

	* themes/default/settings/iconstyles/style-icon-miniicon
	Added styles for Fvwm Themes Form/Script

	* themes/bin/FvwmScript-ThemesCenter:
	French spelling

