2000-10-25  olicha  <olivier.chapuis@free.fr>

	* themes/*/globalfeel:
	* themes/default/theme.cfg:
	rename desktop to globalfeel and use the new spec.

	* scripts/FvwmScript-ConfigCenter:
	* scripts/Makefile.am:
	* bin/fvwm-themes-script.in:
	* bin/fvwm-themes-config.in:
	New FvwmScript for editing globalfeel (and other components in the
	future). The script use a "com loop" in fvwm-themes-script. There is
	a new option (not documented) to fvwm-themes-config which produce 
	the information that fvwm-themes-script need for this "com loop".
	
