2000-10-17  olicha  <olivier.chapuis@free.fr>

	* bin/fvwm-script-config.in:
	--show-themes and --show-components show only the themes with
	component "comp" if --component "comp" is used.
	New options --show-user and --show-site to restrict --show-themes 
	and --show-components  to the user (respectively, the site) dir.
	New option --fvwmscript which force --show-user and --show-site to
	to build output for FvwmScript.

	* themes/default/{bindings,functions-appbind}
	Move MenuFvwmBrowser and MenuFvwmBrowserCached from bindings to 
	functions-appbind

