	added stone.xpm (gray scale), I am not sure whether we need two;
	moved freon_mist.xpm to olicha theme (a background distribution is
	not needed with theme components or could be in a separate package)

	It is not trivial (if at all possible, I am still trying) to make
	a directory instead of a file in CVS. I.e. themes/default/background;
	I think 'commit' is needed between 'delete' and 'add'.

	Uff! This can't be done in CVS. It seems that the only solution
	is to remove this file on the server, even the command
		cvs admin -o1 themes/default/background
	does not help, at least one revision should be remained.

	So, I have added themes/default/background.d instead...

