2000-08-07  migo  <migo@homemail.com>

	* forms/FvwmForm-ThemeSettings:
	removed fvwm-themes-config string.
	Using this form freezes fvwm for me, Ctrl-Alt-Esc helps. Again?

	* forms/FvwmGtk-Themes:
	Temporary config until we have fvwm-themes-gtk (not before 0.4.0).
	We should use FvwmGtk aliases for all our gtk menus, I think,
	or we should implement module config delimiter in fvwm ASAP.
	The name FvwmGtk-Themes means that all gtk-based fvwm-themes dialogs
	may be defined in this file, but this is unclear yet.

	* themes/default/menus:
	Added "AddToMenu MenuFvwmPersonal" to avoid warning.
	Added FvwmGtk-Themes:SettingsDialog.

	When I choose sound-player (play, esd), FvwmEvent (I suppose) does
	not respond (fvwm freezes) and is killed after 30 seconds timeout.

