2000-07-29  migo  <migo@homemail.com>

	* themes/migo/modules/main (FuncFvwmStopThemeModules):
	stop winlist modules

	* bin/fvwm-themes-config.in:
	* themes/default/theme.cfg:
	* themes/default/settings.cfg:
	* themes/*/modules.cfg:
	Implemented 'follows' & 'precedes', unlike 'require' & 'provides'
	the value is another component directly. *-extra@ now use 'follows'.
	Also use 'follows' for some other components instead of 'requires'.

	* themes/multichoice/theme.cfg:
	removed requires+=bindings from colors@

	* themes/olicha/modules/main:FvwmTaskBar:
	added Style "FvwmTaskBar" TitleAtBottom :-)

	* bin/fvwm-themes-config.in (escapeMenuName, getOwnThemeSubMenusRc):
	Fix escaping of & in menu labels, I think it is a bug in fvwm.

	* bin/fvwm-themes-images.in:
	I would really like to check all algorithms, but have no time now.
	Highlight algorithms are bad. Must support rgb:RRRR/GGGG/BBBB format.
	s/--show-xcolorset/--show-xcolorsets/, we show many (all) colorsets.
	Removed traling spaces/tabs, s/size{'tile'}/size{'tiles'}/,
	Some small changes, spelling and comments.
	I use a space between function name and args ($) to distinguish between
	a call and a definition: find 'funcName '. Also in perlsub(1) examples.

	* themes/multichoice/theme.cfg:
	s/Motif/Sky/

	* Makefile.am:
	don't include CVS dirs into distribution

