	* themes/multichoice/background/6:
	commented in 'bggen | xv' variant

	* themes/multichoice/images/background/fvwm-tiger-tail.xpm:
	* themes/multichoice/images/banner/fvwm-red.xpm:
	I forgot we have http://fvwm.org/generated/icon_shots/banner2.gif .
	Added these 2 big files, I am not sure where to use them if at all.

