	cde-sky). Complete the man page.
	
2000-07-27  migo  <migo@homemail.com>

	* configure.in:
	Increased version to 0.2.13.
	Imported fvwm-themes to CVS!

2000-07-26  migo  <migo@homemail.com>

	* themes/cde/background/pattern:
	Moved from incorrect name. I think more paterns may be included
	as options later.

	* bin/fvwm-themes-images.in:
	fixed some indentation and some typos, including an error disabling
	evaluating 'shadow' colors; several perl tweaks.
	Renamed --info-xcolors to --show-xcolors, --info-all-colors to
	--show-xcolorsets, --info-color to --show-color-info; 2 functions
	formatColorInfo[Head]Line().

	* */*:
	% find . | perl -wne 'chomp; if (-s && -T && `tail -1 $_` !~ /\n$/s) \
		{ print "$_\n"; system("echo >>$_") }'
	Make sure all our text files have final EOLN. Please configure your
	editor to force this. In emacs: (setq require-final-newline t).

	* themes/*/background/*:
	Removed comment.

	* themes/migo/background:
	* themes/migo/images/background/cyan-tile.png:
	renamed from .pmg to .png.

	* bin/fvwm-themes-config.in:
	* themes/*/*.cfg:
	Renamed 'global' to 'priority' and 'popup' to 'inline' (inverted
	meaning, and now inline=0, i.e. prior popup=1, is the default).
	Implemented 'option-read-afterward' component value, default is 0.
	Uncommented "+ I DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTheme*" to fix flickering.
	Fixed memory of options.

	* themes/default/theme.cfg:
	Added requires+=colorsets to bindings@ for Shift-Alt-F12 for example.
	Added requires+=MouseXX to buttons@.

	* themes/*/theme.cfg:
	Added this file. Currently if a theme has no theme.cfg, default's
	file is used and it is cached (to get a better performance), so
	--fresh will not work in this case. I may think about this later.

	* themes/default/functions-appbind:
	* themes/settings/stroke/enable:
	Added FuncFvwmQuitVerify instead of QuitVerify form.

	themes/default/menus-user:
	uncommented "xiterm 80x40" menu item

	* themes/default/bindings:
	* themes/*/buttons:
	s/FuncFvwmActionOrWindowsOps/FuncFvwmWindowsOpsOrAction/

	* themes/blackbox/modules/main:FvwmButtons-XX:
	Change global Frame 0 once instead of everywhere in button items.

	* themes/default/modules*:
	Use options for modules (was subcomponents of choices).
	Some renamings, probably not perfect.

	* themes/*/modules*:
	Renamed 'Use Icons' to 'Use Normal Icons' to be less ambiguous,
	s/FuncFvwmStartIcons/FuncFvwmStartNormalIcons/.
	Several other renamings, like s/buttons/buttonbar/.

	* themes/migo/modules*:
	Implemented modules@ options: winlist and normal-icons.
	Heh, module configs are linked to @olicha, and options to @default.

	* */*:
	Total renaming of all module aliases to a new name scheme:
	FvwmModule-SubName. This should be done in fvwm itself too. :-)
	Several (a lot, in fact) corrections during this total renaming.
	Just an idea, how about an alias/wrapper FvwmApplet -> FvwmScript?
	Experimentally install scripts/* and forms/* to flat FT_DATADIR,
	so invocation now does not require scripts/ prefix. I still think
	that flat structure is not good, but probably ok for now, also if
	SearchPath is introduced, we can put FT_DATADIR/scripts to it.

