	patch by Paul D. Smith, die on empty dir value

	* themes/default/theme.cfg:
	* themes/default/settings.cfg:
	* bin/fvwm-themes-config.in:
	* bin/fvwm-themes-config.1:
	Full rewrite of fvwm-themes-config.
	Implemented a basis for the new component definition/dependancy design.
	Managing <mytheme>/theme.cfg definition files.
	Implemented loading/dropping components, component options/choices.
	A new API, see the man page.

	* themes/multichoice/*:
	A new theme with 3 multichoice components: background, cursors, colors.

	* themes/*/desktop:
	Removed obsolete in 2.3.18 style options [Dont]FlipTransient.

