2000-04-17  migo  <migo@homemail.com>

	* doc/FAQ:
	Added "How can I get fvwm config in one file?" and more stroke info.

	* themes/default/menus:
	Added CommandS to regular modules (Alex's request).

	* themes/spruce/colors:
	Module colors now match the original better, I hope.

	* themes/awol/README:
	added a missing file (should contain more info)

	* configure.in, install-sh, missing, mkinstalldirs:
	* bin/fvwm-themes-config.in:
	Added autoconf stuff! Uff...

	* acinclude.m4:
	Added some useful (IMHO) macros.

	* bin/fvwm-themes-config.in:
	Use 'PipeRead' to read itself instead of 'Exec' + 'Wait'.
	Support --site instalation. At the start site's themes-rc (only)
	calls fvwm-themes-config --reset to reset a user version.

	* themes/default/bindings:
	* options/stroke/enabled:
	FuncFvwmResizeOrRaise is now FuncFvwmResizeOrRaiseOrShade.
	This was once suggested by Dominik, to shade on border double click.
	Alt-Mouse3 in borders/title, now like Alt-Mouse3 in window.

	* themes/default/bindings:
	* themes/default/menus:
	Small changes in some main window operation bibdings, now they are
	more windows (and mwm?) like. Added window group raise/lower.

2000-04-07  migo  <migo@homemail.com>

	* Makefile:
	* README:
	Fixed a non-fatal error when the current personal theme is not found.
	Support for installing in another place (by $FVWM_USERHOME).

