	are now read in this file.
	options/current/sound is read in themes/default/sound

	* options/gnome/anotherlevel-menu:
	* bin/fvwm-themes-config:
	Added AnotherLevel menu as a gnome option (wmconfig which generate
	directly such a fvwm2 menu is not usable since the menus are not
	distroyed ...)

